6:
Hmm... Are these prices reasonable,
I wonder...
13:
Good day, Stella. Alk. Thank you
once again for the other day.
18:
Always happy to help. Are you out
shopping?
21:
Yes, I am attempting to purchase
ingredients for dinner.
24:
However, I am having some trouble,
as I am not yet used to Palpebra's
markets.
26:
Would you happen to know any
shops with reasonable prices in the
area?
29:
You bet we do. We're in the middle
of shopping for dinner too, actually.
32:
You are more than welcome to join
us.
43:
I am astonished that such quality
ingredients could be purchased for
a good price.
46:
Palpebra's a bustling center of
trade. There are enough shops and
products here to make anyone's
head spin.
48:
Makes it hard to find the good shops
without the proper know-how.
51: I see. I will keep this in mind.
58:
S-somebody stop that man! He's a
thief!
61: Sorry, Stella, look after our stuff!
65:
Alk, meager though my powers may
be, allow me to assist.
70:
Wow, your magic really is
something, Kokkoro! I feel as swift as
the wind!
75:
Stealing from others is a crime.
Acknowledge your wrongdoing, and
turn yourself in quietly.
78: Cut the crap and piss off, kid!
80:
It appears that you have no
intention of repenting.
83:
You won't make any friends with
that kind of attitude, you know.
93:
I did not expect so many
townspeople to shower us with gifts...
98:
Well, they were pretty impressed.
Plus they wanted to show their
appreciation.
101:
I am a little embarrassed, but also
relieved as my coin purse is in dire
straits at the moment.
104:
Though... there are quite a few
ingredients in here that I have never
seen before. I am unsure how to
prepare them.
107:
Oh. Guess it makes sense you
wouldn't know what to do with stuff
that doesn't exist in Landosol.
110: How about I show you the ropes?
115:
I see you are very skilled at cooking,
Alk. Your practiced movements
indicate as much.
119:
He's had to spend a lot of time in
here, considering how often we rely
on him for meals.
124: I do it because I enjoy it though.
129:
It smells good. I am starting to get
hungry.
134:
Hehe, the food will be ready
momentarily. Just be patient a little
while longer, all right?
142:
You appeared so earnestly excited, I
instinctually treated you as I would a
child...
149:
Are those seasonings also native to
Palpebra?
153:
Nah, we brought these home from
another world.
156:
I see... I presume you utilized the
World Flipper then.
157:
To be honest, I am still having a
hard time wrapping my head
around the existence of such an
apparatus.
163:
If you're so curious, why not join us
the next time we embark on an
adventure?
167:
That's a good idea. While we're at it,
we might even find a way to get you
home to Landosol.
172:
Are you sure it is all right for me to
accompany you?
175:
Of course. Stella agrees as well, I'm
sure.
Stella?
189:
I am being patient like Kokkoro
instructed.
194:
And how patient you have been. You
are a good listener.
198:
Good girl. You deserve all of the
head pats...
206:
Hehe, you are very welcome. It is the
least I can do after you have so
graciously allowed me into your
home.
209:
You are always welcome here,
Kokkoro.
